{
  "stem": "7739.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyways, just bedlam, you know, everybody trying to stay together with their families, more or less.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the market square was full of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Although we were one of the first ones to go there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As the day progressed, we went out to market square.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My brother went to these Christian people, by the name of Glina, on the same street we lived, except it was further down nearly out of town.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he went there, it was pre-arranged.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we stayed in the market square, and people were coming out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "When the people were full, when the market square was full already, and we were surrounded by all these soldiers, the fellow in charge of the employment in this-- in these Hermann Goering worker, and these ammunition factories-- barked out an order to all those who are holding work permits should step out.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father stepped out, I stepped out, my brother wasn't there, because he was working the night shift.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he was in the factories, and they didn't-- they weren't allowed to go back home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They kept them there for the day of expulsion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, this was just to illustrate a quirk of fate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a rucksack with me, and I stepped out together with my father, and we were on the way.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said all those workers have to assemble on the sidewalk, against the houses at the end of the square.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the fellow from the [NON-ENGLISH], from the employment, stopped me on the way there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He stopped me and he says to me, how old are you?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, I'm 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew him by the name, and I called him Herr Schwertner-- he was in civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wasn't a soldier.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
